[l] Chinas Wachstum geht voellig ueberraschend auch nicht unendlich so weiter.Back in 2009, as China unleashed a massive fiscal stimulus and investment spree in response to the global financial crisis, the rest of the world was all too willing to believe the impossible. Aided by consultant research predicting decades of explosive growth, companies placed huge bets on China and expected to ride the never-ending boom to riches.Wie, Wunder gibt es gar nicht?! Moan ey! Da werden die Investoren aber unzufrieden sein!
